### =========================================
### 2. RAG BAZASINI YARATISH: .docx hujjatni yuklash (Multipart Form-Data)
# Eslatma: mini_mehnat_kodeksi.docx fayli ushbu .http fayl bilan bitta papkada turishi kerak!
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/legal-documents/upload
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ1a3RhbW92OTE5OEBtYWlsLnJ1Iiwicm9sZXMiOiJST0xFX1VTRVIsUk9MRV9TVVBFUkFETUlOIiwiaWQiOiI5IiwiaWF0IjoxNzgxODYwNDg4LCJleHAiOjE3ODE5NDY4ODh9.gyHiJ0_8BRRUG0so78Gt6CaXM4o2PBRbdaSbj2vwJDdB6B90MiDUk5f9Uf7Z91B7SdOBNwAWjbZowPyt-hRaUA
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="mini_mehnat_kodeksi.docx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document

< ./mini_mehnat_kodeksi.docx
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

CODE
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="docNumber"

MK-2022
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="docDate"

2022-10-28
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

O'zbekiston Respublikasining Mehnat Kodeksi (Mini)
--WebAppBoundary--

### Kutilayotgan natija: 200 OK. 
### DIQQAT: Shu so'rovni jo'natgach, IDE konsoliga qarab turing. 
### Orqa fonda "Gemini Embedding" ishlab, vektorlar bazaga yozilishini (Async) 3-4 soniya kuting.


### =========================================
### 3. YANGI AI CHAT YARATISH (Test qilish uchun xona)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ai-chats
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "RAG Test Chat"
}
### Kutilayotgan natija: Chat yaratiladi. Qaytgan "id" ni eng tepasidagi @chatId ga yozing!


### =========================================
### 4. TEST 1: RAG QIDIRUV (Aniq qonun bo'yicha savol)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ai-chats/{{chatId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content": "Mening ukam 15 yoshda, u qonuniy ishga kirsa bo'ladimi? Mehnat qonunchiligida nima deyilgan?"
}
### Kutilayotgan natija: AI osmondan olib emas, aynan siz yuklagan fayldagi 15-moddaga tayanib, 
### "Ota-onasining yozma roziligi bilan ishga qabul qilinishi mumkin" deb javob beradi. 
### Backend loglarida HNSW qidiruvi ishlaganini ko'rasiz. AiResponse dagi "ragUsed" = true bo'ladi.


### =========================================
### 5. TEST 2: GIBRID REJIM (Bazada yo'q qonun bo'yicha savol)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ai-chats/{{chatId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content": "Soliq tekshiruvi qanday qoidalarga asosan o'tkaziladi? Jarimalar qancha?"
}
### Kutilayotgan natija: Bazamizda Soliq kodeksi yo'q. Qidiruv hech narsa topa olmaydi. 
### AI umumiy bilimiga tayanib javob yozadi va oxiriga MAJBURIY DISCLAIMER qo'shadi: 
### "Bu ma'lumot umumiy xarakterga ega... advokat bilan maslahatlashing...". 
### AiResponse dagi "ragUsed" = false bo'ladi.


### =========================================
### 6. TEST 3: AQLLI YANGILASH (Hash Diffing Testi)
# Qadamlar:
# 1. Kompyuteringizdagi 'mini_mehnat_kodeksi.docx' faylini oching.
# 2. Ichidagi "o'n besh yoshga to'lgan" degan so'zni "O'N TO'RT YOSHGA TO'LGAN" deb o'zgartirib, saqlang.
# 3. Va ushbu so'rovni qayta yuboring (docNumber eski MK-2023 ligicha qoladi):

POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/legal-documents/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="mini_mehnat_kodeksi.docx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document

< ./mini_mehnat_kodeksi.docx
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

CODE
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="docNumber"

MK-2023
--WebAppBoundary--

### Kutilayotgan natija: Dastur Exception tashlamaydi! U eski "MK-2023" ni topadi.
### 1-moddani o'zgarishsiz qoldiradi, faqat 15-moddani o'chiring yangisini bazaga yozadi. 
### Asosiy hujjat statusi "PARTIALLY_AMENDED" ga aylanadi. 
### Buni sinash uchun 4-so'rovni (TEST 1) yana jo'natib ko'ring, AI endi "14 yosh" deb javob berishni boshlaydi!